                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 812.00/17166</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Consular Agent <persName type="from">Williams</persName> to
                        the <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram—Extract]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Consular Agency</hi>, <lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Torreon</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1916-01-27">
                            <hi rend="italic">January 27, 1916</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Since my telegram January 15, midnight, expropriation foreign-owned cotton
                    stopped, due to representations made by representatives German Government and
                    French Government.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Williams</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
